org.netbeans.modules.java.j2seproject.api

Interface J2SEBuildPropertiesProvider


  • public interface J2SEBuildPropertiesProvider
    Allows J2SE project extensions to supply additional build properties. The instances are registered in project Lookup.
    Since:
    1.71
    See Also:
    ProjectServiceProvider
